{"_path":"/prestations/semelles","_dir":"prestations","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"Semelles","description":"C’est la science qui étudie la prévention, le diagnostic et la prise en charge des pathologies du pied et de l’appareil locomoteur.","image":{"src":"/semelles.webp"},"date":"2024-08-01T00:00:00.000Z","badge":{"label":"Podologie"},"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Je réalise des semelles orthopédiques à la demande du médecin, je peux aussi en prescrire (mais vous ne serez pas remboursés)."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Lors du premier rendez-vous, je réalise un examen clinique complet :"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Interrogatoire"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Examen statique global sur podoscope et sur plateforme podobarométrique"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Examen dynamique"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Il existe différents types de semelles pour différents types de pathologies pour différents patients ayants des âges et des activités différentes.Peaks and Valleys - Nature's Masterpiece"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"les-semelles-thermoformées"},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Les semelles thermoformées"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Elles sont moulées sur le pied du patient et ont une action biomécanique."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Il existe énormément de matériaux qui me permettent de faire des semelles efficaces et confortables en fonction de chaque pathologie et de chaque patient."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Pour qui :"}]},{"type":"text","value":" je ne fais ce type de semelles que chez l’adulte ou l’adolescent, le sportif et les personnes qui recherchent du confort, personnes âgées, diabétiques…"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Pour quoi :"}]},{"type":"text","value":" talalgie, aponévrosite plantaire (épine calcanéenne), douleur de l’avant pied, problèmes de genoux, tendinite de la patte d’oie, syndrome de l’essuie-glace, périsostite tibiale, instabilité de cheville, fonte du capiton plantaire, problèmes de dos, inégalité vraie des membres inférieurs…"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"div","props":{"className":["flex","space-x-4","items-center","justify-between"]},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"div","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"semelle thermophormées bleues","className":["rounded-lg"],"height":400,"src":"/semelle_thermo_1.jpg","width":400},"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"div","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"semelle thermophormées vertes","className":["rounded-lg"],"height":400,"src":"/semelle_thermo_2.jpg","width":400},"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"div","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"semelle thermophormées rouges","className":["rounded-lg"],"height":400,"src":"/semelle_thermo_3.jpg","width":400},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"les-semelles-proprioceptives"},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Les semelles proprioceptives"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Ce sont des semelles fines, les calles ne font pas plus de 4 mm, elles agissent sur les récepteurs des muscles et des tendons qu’elles vont stimuler ou inhiber et ainsi agir comme une rééducation."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Pour qui :"}]},{"type":"text","value":" les enfants et les adultes."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Pour quoi :"}]},{"type":"text","value":" les pieds plats, les pieds creux, en dehors ou en dedans, mais elles agissent aussi plus haut pour aider à corriger un trouble postural et ainsi soulager des maux de genoux, de bassin, de dos…"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"div","props":{"className":["flex","space-x-4","items-center","justify-between"]},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"div","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"semelles proprioceptives 1","className":["rounded-lg"],"height":400,"src":"/semelle_proprio_1.jpg","width":400},"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"div","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"semelles proprioceptives 2","className":["rounded-lg"],"height":400,"src":"/semelle_proprio_2.jpg","width":400},"children":[]}]}]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"les-semelles-thermoformées","depth":2,"text":"Les semelles thermoformées"},{"id":"les-semelles-proprioceptives","depth":2,"text":"Les semelles proprioceptives"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:1.prestations:3.semelles.md","_source":"content","_file":"1.prestations/3.semelles.md","_stem":"1.prestations/3.semelles","_extension":"md"}